  p.w3-xlarge
  button.w3-button.w3-black.w3-padding-large.w3-large.w3-hover-white.w3-margin-top(onclick="location.href='register.html'" type='button') Get Started
// First Grid
.w3-row-padding.w3-padding-64.w3-container
  .w3-content
    .w3-twothird
      h1 Our Mission
      h5.w3-padding-32
        | According to the National Center for Missing and Exploited Children 2020 Report, approximately 82% of AMBER Alerts had vehicle involvement and 43% of AMBER Alert success stories resulted from recognizing a vehicle. 
      p.w3-text-grey
        | Electri's mission is to leverage the increasingly prevalent dashboard cameras and autonomous cars driving on the roads today in order to maximize the successful resolutions of AMBER Alerts.
        | By automating responses to active AMBER Alerts, we not only provide a hands-free, easy-to-use service but also drastically increase the data sourcing capabilities in an attempt to save lives as quickly and efficiently as possible. 
